  dialogId: dlg_rumor_story
  entries:
  - speaker: Iris, Rumor Keeper
    line: Ferry hands, scavengers, and ridge climbers all tell the same lie in different words. Something is calling them uphill.
    choiceNextIds: []
  - speaker: Iris, Rumor Keeper
    line: Take my leads seriously and you will always reach the next storm before the panic does.
